reviewText: One of the best shows I have ever seen
This blu ray is rated for all regions, but would not play. Doesn't seem playable in the us, at least for me. Buyer beware. Amazon was great and issued a refund but exercise caution before you buy
I had to give this 1 star because it would not play in my Blu-ray player. Quite sad because it is a fantastic show! Info said it was for ALL REGIONS but that isn't accurate.
This is one of the best shows I've seen. The characters while quirky are very likable. Gavin and Stacy offers nearly non stop laughter and allows you to escape your life a half an hour at a time.
I just love this show from the UK!  The characters are so quirkey and genuine!  Great Story and I love the lifestyle!
This is a great series and a great one that can be watched again and again. It is a feel good series. You become absorbed with each character more and more as the series continues on. LOVE IT!

This is a 50hz version that my new Panasonic BD won't play. Or my older one either.
Now if I want one that will play (hopefully) I will have to pay 3x as much. Gave it a 3, I had to give a rating.
